Class ListItem

  • Object
    • ListItem

  • public class ListItem
extends Object
    Define an item in a ScrollList. This element is typically encapsulated in a ScrollListGadget. It is similar to a dropdown element, but typically has a more fancy look. This makes it great for use in in-game screens, while a dropdown element is reserved for use in the editor.
